 aquifer? How much lake water would have been stored in that aquifer in
 that same period?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Using the expression and setting 
\begin_inset Formula $n=2$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $A=3$
\end_inset

