\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 for given times.
 Alternatively, we can make graphs of 
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $Q$
\end_inset

 as a function of time for given values of 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

.
 The results are shown in figure  
