LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:Qr-over-Q0"

\end_inset

 firstly as a function of 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

 for different values of 
\begin_inset Formula $r$
\end_inset

.
 Of course, all curves would coincide to a single line if plotted versus
 
\begin_inset Formula $t/r^{2}$
\end_inset

 or 
\begin_inset Formula $1/u$
\end_inset

 (not shown).
 The figures 
